overview: Kendra Lust runs a high end massage parlor that caters to more than just a good sports rub down. Happy endings abound for a few select customers. But when her top employee quits, she scrambles to find a young, handsome masseur to cater to her wealthy female clients.
tagline: Your Pleasure, Comfort, And Relaxation Is In Their Hands!
title: The Masseuse 5
